Society.Relationships:
Kaortis created [[rukanyr]]s and [[skybleeder]]s as thralls to aid and further their goal of corrupting the Material plane, and [[kaortic hulk]]s as shock troops. They also brought with them creatures such as [[half-farspawn]], [[amoebic crawler]]s, [[nightseed]]s, and [[urquirsh]] back from the Far Realm.<ref>{{Cite dragon/330/Enter the Far Realm}}
